Plots supplementary MCAR 20 n1000

Paulina von Stackelberg

28 4 2021

In this document, you can find plots generated for n=1000, MCAR, 20 covariates.

library(tidyverse)
MCAR_2_lasso20 <- readRDS("MCAR_2_lasso")
MCAR_4_lasso20 <- readRDS("MCAR_4_lasso")
MCAR_6_lasso20 <- readRDS("MCAR_6_lasso")
MCAR_8_lasso20 <- readRDS("MCAR_8_lasso")

MCAR_2_ridge20 <- readRDS("MCAR_2_ridge")
MCAR_4_ridge20 <- readRDS("MCAR_4_ridge")
MCAR_6_ridge20 <- readRDS("MCAR_6_ridge")
MCAR_8_ridge20 <- readRDS("MCAR_8_ridge")
cond1_MCAR2_lasso <- MCAR_2_lasso20[["Results_cond1"]] %>% lapply(., FUN=function(i) sapply(i, colMeans, na.rm=T)) %>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% do.call(rbind, .) %>% as.data.frame(.,) %>%
  mutate(condition= 'MI-bef(y)')

cond2_MCAR2_lasso <- MCAR_2_lasso20[["Results_cond2"]] %>% lapply(., FUN = function(i) do.call(rbind, i)) %>% lapply(., FUN=function(i) sapply(i, colMeans, na.rm=T)) %>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% lapply(., FUN= colMeans, na.rm=T)%>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% do.call(rbind, .)%>% as.data.frame(.,)%>%
  mutate(condition = 'MI-bef(-y)')

cond3_MCAR2_lasso <- MCAR_2_lasso20[["Results_cond3"]] %>% lapply(., FUN = function(i) do.call(rbind, i)) %>% lapply(., FUN=function(i) sapply(i, colMeans, na.rm=T)) %>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% lapply(., FUN= colMeans, na.rm=T)%>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% do.call(rbind, .)%>%as.data.frame(.,)%>%
  mutate(condition = 'MI-CVreuse')

cond4_MCAR2_lasso <- MCAR_2_lasso20[["Results_cond4"]] %>% lapply(., FUN = function(i) do.call(rbind, i)) %>% lapply(., FUN=function(i) sapply(i, colMeans, na.rm=T)) %>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% lapply(., FUN= colMeans, na.rm=T)%>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% do.call(rbind, .)%>%as.data.frame(.,)%>%
  mutate(condition = 'MI-CVsep')

complete_MCAR2_lasso <- MCAR_2_lasso20[["results_comp"]] %>% lapply(., FUN=function(i) sapply(i, colMeans, na.rm=T)) %>% lapply(., FUN = t) %>% do.call(rbind, .)%>%as.data.frame(.,)%>%
  mutate(condition = 'complete')

merged_data_2 <- rbind(cond1_MCAR2_lasso, cond2_MCAR2_lasso, cond3_MCAR2_lasso, cond4_MCAR2_lasso, complete_MCAR2_lasso)

merged_data_24_ridgeLasso <- rbind(merged_data_24_ridge, merged_data_24_lasso)

AUC_24_ridgeLasso <- ggplot(data = merged_data_24_ridgeLasso, aes(x=as.factor(mis_prop), y=AUC, fill = condition)) +
             geom_boxplot()+ xlab("Missingness proportion") + ylab("AUC")+
  facet_wrap(~ model)+ theme(axis.title.x = element_blank()) + scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0.5,1, by =0.1))+
  ylim(0.5,0.95)

2. Plots for the calibration slope and intercept

LASSO and Ridge, cor 0.3

merged_data_68_ridgeLasso <- rbind(merged_data_68_ridge, merged_data_68_lasso)

calb0_68_ridgeLasso <- ggplot(data = merged_data_68_ridgeLasso, aes(x=as.factor(mis_prop), y=cal_b0, fill = condition)) +
             geom_boxplot()+ xlab("Missingness proportion") + ylab("calibration intercept")+
  facet_wrap(~ model)+ theme(axis.title.x = element_blank())+
